fields.title: Django Battleships
fields.description: A web application that allows two registered users to play a game of battleships against each other.
fields.requirements:
Users must be able to register and login.

Users must be able to customize a profile.

Wins and losses must be tracked per user.

fields.name: Django Developer
fields.description:
Must be relatively proficient in the Python programming language/syntax.
Must have had experience in building completing at least 1 Django Application.
Must fluently know how to interact with HTML/CSS

fields.name: Front-End Design Lead
fields.description:
Overseer of all Front End design.

Must have basic understanding of Python programming language.

fields.name: JavaScript Developer
fields.description:
Must be proficient in JavaScript.
Must have basic experience uses frameworks like React and Angular.
